'''克卜勒452b'''（'''Kepler-452b'''），是一顆圍繞著[[G型主序星|G型主序星]][[克卜勒452|克卜勒452]]的太陽系外行星。由[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]團隊發現，並由[[美国国家航空航天局|NASA]]於2015年7月23日公布。是已知[[類地行星|類地行星]]中，第一顆潜在軌道位於與[[太陽|太陽]]相似的[[适居带|恆星舒適帶]]上的[[超级地球|超级地球]]<ref name="Chou">{{cite press release|last1 = Chou|first1 = Felicia|last2 = Johnson|first2 = Michelle|title = NASA’s Kepler Mission Discovers Bigger, Older Cousin to Earth|url = http://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-kepler-mission-discovers-bigger-older-cousin-to-earth|accessdate = 23 July 2015|agency = NASA|date = 23 July 2015|archive-date = 2015-10-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151007035447/http://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-kepler-mission-discovers-bigger-older-cousin-to-earth/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。使用[[地球相似指數|地球相似指數]]衡量，它是第6个最像地球的行星。

這顆行星距離[[太阳系|太陽系]]1,400光年；以目前人類所發射最快的飛行器[[新視野號|新視野號]]的速度也需要2,580萬年才能到達。<ref name="bno">{{cite web|url = http://bnonews.com/news/index.php/news/id961|script-title = en:NASA telescope discovers Earth-like planet in star’s ‘habitable zone’|date = 23 July 2015|work = [[BNO_News|BNO News]]|accessdate = 23 July 2015|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042706/http://bnonews.com/news/index.php/news/id961|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==特性==
克卜勒-452b行星的公转轨迹略大于地球的[[公转|公转]]轨迹。公转一周需385天。<ref name=Overbye>{{cite news|last1=Overbye|first1=Dennis|script-title=en:Kepler Data Reveals What Might Be Best ‘Goldilocks’ Planet Yet|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/24/science/space/kepler-data-reveals-what-might-be-best-goldilocks-planet-yet.html?_r=0|accessdate=23 July 2015|work=The New York Times|date=23 July 2015|archive-date=2015-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150726104949/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/24/science/space/kepler-data-reveals-what-might-be-best-goldilocks-planet-yet.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>目前没有证据证明开普勒452b上面有生命，因为开普勒望远镜只负责照相，没有办法近距离观测行星。<ref>{{cite news|title=NASA发现"另一个地球":相似指数0.98 或有流动水|url=http://news.163.com/15/0724/00/AV8FNH640001121M.html|accessdate=23 July 2015|work=网易|date=23 July 2015|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724024307/http://news.163.com/15/0724/00/AV8FNH640001121M.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>它的直徑比地球大60%，體積為地球的5倍，地表的重力是地球的兩倍，跟其恆星的距離與地球和太陽的距離相約，它的恆星比太陽老15億年，光度為太陽的1.2倍。<ref>{{cite news|title=太空總署發現最似地球星體|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20150724/19230722?_ga=1.1713079.768165092.1435212783|accessdate=24 July 2015|work=[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]|date=24 July 2015|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724075439/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20150724/19230722?_ga=1.1713079.768165092.1435212783|dead-url=no}}</ref>但[[開普勒452|開普勒452]]正邁向死亡，若開普勒452b是一顆岩石星球的話，那麼開普勒452增強散發的能量未來將把開普勒452b上可能存在的海洋和任何水份蒸發掉，地球在數十億年之後，也可能出現類似情況。<ref>{{cite news|title=NASA宣佈 發現與地球極相似行星|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20150724/54008650|accessdate=24 July 2015|work=[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]|date=24 July 2015|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724203651/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20150724/54008650|dead-url=no}}</ref>

